TriggerLogic.Name: GUI Message
TriggerLogic.Message: Dead units (and buildings) leave wrecks in the spot where they die. These wrecks contain a lot of metal. In this mission you cannot build mexes and you must kill enemy units to get metal. Your objective is to find and destory the enemy geothermal power plant in the east.

TriggerLogic.Name: Marker
TriggerLogic.Text: You can reclaim wrecks with your commander and with constructors.
Select 'reclaim' from the units menu, then click and drag to reclaim within a given area.
